            "text": "Welcome! This workspace runs entirely in the browser so you can explore layouts without wiring a backend.\\n\\nTips:\\n• Drag/resize tiles, or duplicate them with the copy icon.\\n• Click the settings gear on any widget to adjust refresh timing, colors, or copy text.\\n• Use the sidebar to add/remove figures, import/export layouts, and load plugin bundles.",
